Author:
Vol / Page:  3/25
Edition:
Quote:  Jingling Johnny: Originally a swagman but also another name for a hand shearer. Many of the old shearers carried their swags from shed to shed and no doubt their shears and billycans jingled as they walked.
Notes:  (Wallace Shearing Glossary)
